Package: eventloop
Type: Package
Title: Event Loop for Interactive Realtime Rendering
Version: 0.1.1
Author: mikefc
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mike", "FC", email = "mikefc@coolbutuseless.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
  )
Maintainer: mikefc <mikefc@coolbutuseless.com>
Description: An event loop with non-blocking keyboard and mouse
    events.  This is only possible on graphics devices which support the
    'onIdle' callback i.e. x11() devices on macOS and *nux.
